beer_brewer_name: Port Brewing Co / The Lost Abbey
review_blob: Love port brewing, great coffee notes from this smooth brown ale. Thick chocolaty head that stays for the full glass

review_blob: If its a fruit beer, I want to taste the fruit. Not sweet which is good, but could use more fruit
Sweet start and the finish is odd. Not the typical maltyness of an american Oktoberfest
